text: Impact Academy is an American online-based school that is part of the Henry County School System in the Georgia Public School System. It serves all of Henry County Schools, from middle to high school. Impact Academy was founded in the fall of 2012. It is located between Henry County High School and the technology service building just off the McDonough, Georgia square. ==Student demographics== *Male: 349 *Female: 260 Total number of students: 609 ==References== *http://schoolwires.henry.k12.ga.us/Domain/3055 Category:Schools in Georgia (U.S. state)
